&lt;li&gt;Summary- Security attacks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active attack
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;involves data modification or the creation of a false stream, e.g.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;masquerade, replay, modification of messages, man-in-the-middle (MITM) and DoS/DDoS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passive attack
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;attempts to learn or make use of information from the system but does not affect system resources, e.g. traffic analysis, release of information contents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

